snippet.title: Arena Breakout - Official Season 3 Announcement Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: Check out the teaser trailer for Season 3 of Arena Breakout for a peek at what's coming in the tactical extraction shooter game. In Season 3, raid the TV Station and discover Kamona's most dangerous secret. Season 3 of Arena Breakout kicks off on January 19, 2024. Arena Breakout is available now on iOS and Android.
